  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/28/bikinis-surfboards-and-battle-axes-hawaii-loosens-long-strict-weapons-laws-after-court-ruling.webp" alt="Bikinis, surfboards and battle-axes? Hawaii loosens long-strict weapons laws after court ruling" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Bikinis, surfboards and battle-axes? Hawaii loosens long-strict weapons laws after court ruling</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      HONOLULU (AP) — Hawaii's tourist hotspot of Waikiki is known for bikinis, shopping and surfboards. But resident Andrew Roberts has recently introduced a different item on evening walks through his neighborhood: a long-poled battle-axe.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/28/bikinis-surfboards-and-battle-axes-hawaii-loosens-long-strict-weapons-laws-after-court-ruling/"  >(JENNIFER SINCO KELLEHER, Associated Press, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
