        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Former WWE world champion, WrestleMania headliner dies</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Former WWE world champion Sidney Eudy, who wrestled under the names Sycho Sid, Sid Vicious and Sid Justice, has died.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/26/former-wwe-world-champion-wrestlemania-headliner-dies/"  >(Michael Reiner, KRON4)</a>
    </p>
