    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Could intermittent fasting raise the risk of colon cancer?</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Intermittent fasting involves cycling between periods of fasting and eating, like limiting eating to specific hours.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/27/could-intermittent-fasting-raise-the-risk-of-colon-cancer/"  >(Taylor Delandro, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
