      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/27/judge-in-texas-orders-pause-on-biden-program-that-offers-legal-status-to-spouses-of-us-citizens/"  >(VALERIE GONZALEZ, Associated Press, ABC 4)</a>
