        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">ActBlue is a Democratic fundraising juggernaut&#8212;and now conservatives are coming for it</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Since becoming the presumptive Democratic nominee for President—and as of this month, the actual Democratic nominee for president—Vice President Kamala Harris has blasted past fundraising records. Within 24 hours of President Joe Biden’s endorsement in July, her campaign raised $81 million.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/08/27/actblue-is-a-democratic-fundraising-juggernaut-and-now-conservatives-are-coming-for-it/"  >(Issie Lapowsky, Fast Company)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 27 Aug 2024 09:00:00 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 27 Aug 2024 09:00:00 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Info World">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/tech/2024/08/27/quantum-computing-attacks-on-cloud-based-systems.webp" alt="Quantum computing attacks on cloud-based systems" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Quantum computing attacks on cloud-based systems</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Quantum-resistant cryptography has become an increasingly urgent topic as the threat posed by quantum computing continues to grow. The U.S. National Institute of Standards and Technology (NIST) recently released the first set of finalized algorithms designed to withstand quantum computer attacks.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/08/27/quantum-computing-attacks-on-cloud-based-systems/"  >(Info World)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 28 Aug 2024 23:06:42 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 28 Aug 2024 23:06:42 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="MICHAEL LIEDTKE, Associated Press, KRON4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
