        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">CrowdStrike estimates the tech meltdown caused by its bungling left a $60 million dent in its sales</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Cybersecurity specialist CrowdStrike Holdings on Wednesday estimated it absorbed a roughly $60 million blow to its sales pipeline last month after its botched handling of a software update triggered a technology meltdown that stranded thousands of people in airports in addition to other exasperating
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/08/28/crowdstrike-estimates-the-tech-meltdown-caused-by-its-bungling-left-a-60-million-dent-in-its-sales/"  >(MICHAEL LIEDTKE, Associated Press, KRON4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
