        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Data center construction skyrockets as vacancies drop</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Growing demand for AI workloads and high-power computing capabilities is putting pressure on the data center market. Data center construction is hitting record highs, while vacancies are dropping to record lows, according to data from CBRE Group.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/08/26/data-center-construction-skyrockets-as-vacancies-drop/"  >(Network World)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
