    <h3 itemprop="headline">Dodgers' Shohei Ohtani throws off a mound for 1st time since elbow surgery last fall</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Shohei Ohtani threw off a mound Saturday for the first time since having elbow surgery last year that has kept the Los Angeles Dodgers superstar from pitching this season.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/25/dodgers-shohei-ohtani-throws-off-a-mound-for-1st-time-since-elbow-surgery-last-fall/"  >(Associated Press, Fox 5)</a>
