    <p itemprop="text">
      OutKick host Dan Dakich defended Colorado Buffaloes head football coach Deion Sanders after Sanders was criticized for banning a columnist from asking questions at press conferences.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/28/outkicks-dan-dakich-defends-deion-sanders-amid-latest-criticism-toward-colorado-coach/"  >(Fox News)</a>
