    <h3 itemprop="headline">ESPN: Lions sign veteran wide receiver, Detroit native Allen Robinson II to practice squad</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Detroit Lions continue to add some much-needed depth to their receiving core, as ESPN Fantasy Football and NFL Draft Analyst Field Yates reports that Allen Robinson II has signed to the practice squad.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/28/espn-lions-sign-veteran-wide-receiver-detroit-native-allen-robinson-ii-to-practice-squad/"  >(Brandon Carr, Local 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
