        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Suzuki, Swanson homer as the Cubs beat the Pirates 9-5 to move above .500</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      PITTSBURGH (AP) — Seiya Suzuki and Dansby Swanson homered during Chicago's five-run fourth inning, and the Cubs beat the Pittsburgh Pirates 9-5 on Tuesday night to move over .500 for the first time since May 28.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/28/suzuki-swanson-homer-as-the-cubs-beat-the-pirates-9-5-to-move-above-500/"  >(Associated Press, WGN 9)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 28 Aug 2024 04:04:20 GMT">
