  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/sports/2024/08/28/no-1-swiatek-shakes-off-tough-test-to-win-opening-round-match-at-the-us-open.webp" alt="US Open: Naomi Osaka gets her first top-10 win in more than four years by defeating Ostapenko" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">US Open: Naomi Osaka gets her first top-10 win in more than four years by defeating Ostapenko</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      NEW YORK (AP) — A year ago, still on maternity leave and still unsure when she would play elite tennis again, Naomi Osaka visited the U.S. Open to appear with Michael Phelps for a discussion about mental health. While at the site, she sat in the stands to watch one of Coco Gauff's matches.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/28/no-1-swiatek-shakes-off-tough-test-to-win-opening-round-match-at-the-us-open/"  >(HOWARD FENDRICH, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
