    <h3 itemprop="headline">NASCAR at Daytona: Drama, crashes fill race with surprise winner</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The COKE ZERO SUGAR 400 race was filled with drama and crashing at the Daytona International Speedway on Saturday night.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/25/nascar-at-daytona-drama-crashes-fill-race-with-surprise-winner/"  >(Jeff Patterson, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
