      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/23/trump-ends-border-interview-citing-safety-concerns-amid-search-for-death-threat-suspect.webp" alt="Trump ends border interview citing safety concerns amid search for death threat suspect" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Trump ends border interview citing safety concerns amid search for death threat suspect</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Former President Donald Trump was whisked away from a NewsNation interview when he was told that things were not safe
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/23/trump-ends-border-interview-citing-safety-concerns-amid-search-for-death-threat-suspect/"  >(Jeff Arnold, Fox 5)</a>
    </p>
