<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 27 Aug 2024 00:10:03 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 27 Aug 2024 00:10:03 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="The Associated Press, MPR News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/27/trump-rebukes-harris-and-biden-on-anniversary-of-afghanistan-bombing.webp" alt="Trump rebukes Harris and Biden on anniversary of Afghanistan bombing that killed 13 service members" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Trump rebukes Harris and Biden on anniversary of Afghanistan bombing that killed 13 service members</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Former President Donald Trump is tying Vice President Kamala Harris to the chaotic Afghanistan War withdrawal on the third anniversary of the suicide bombing that killed 13 U.S. service members.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/27/trump-rebukes-harris-and-biden-on-anniversary-of-afghanistan-bombing/"  >(The Associated Press, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 26 Aug 2024 14:37:06 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 26 Aug 2024 14:37:06 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Julia Shapero, Fox 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/26/trump-musk-probably-too-busy-to-serve-in-cabinet-but-could-consult.webp" alt="Trump: Musk probably too busy to serve in Cabinet, but could 'consult'" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Trump: Musk probably too busy to serve in Cabinet, but could 'consult'</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Former President Donald Trump said Tesla CEO Elon Musk would probably be too busy to serve in his Cabinet if he wins the election in November but suggested the billionaire tech mogul could “consult.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/26/trump-musk-probably-too-busy-to-serve-in-cabinet-but-could-consult/"  >(Julia Shapero, Fox 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 28 Aug 2024 20:52:34 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 28 Aug 2024 20:52:34 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="The Associated Press, MPR News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/28/trump-campaign-was-warned-not-to-take-photos-at-arlington.webp" alt="Trump campaign was warned not to take photos at Arlington before altercation, defense official says" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Trump campaign was warned not to take photos at Arlington before altercation, defense official says</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Donald Trump’s campaign was warned about not taking photographs before an altercation at Arlington National Cemetery during a wreath-laying ceremony earlier this week to honor service members killed in the Afghanistan War withdrawal, a defense official told The Associated Press on Wednesday.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/28/trump-campaign-was-warned-not-to-take-photos-at-arlington/"  >(The Associated Press, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 23 Aug 2024 18:13:08 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 23 Aug 2024 18:13:08 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Alix Martichoux, WFLA, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/23/live-will-rfk-jr-drop-out-and-endorse-trump.webp" alt="RFK suspends 2024 campaign, joins Trump at rally" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">RFK suspends 2024 campaign, joins Trump at rally</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      After days of speculation, Robert F. Kennedy Jr. pulled himself out of the 2024 presidential race on Friday — at least in a few battleground election states.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/23/live-will-rfk-jr-drop-out-and-endorse-trump/"  >(Alix Martichoux, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 22 Aug 2024 15:25:54 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 22 Aug 2024 15:25:54 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="The Associated Press, WFLA, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/22/questions-remain-as-tech-company-takes-blame-for-glitch-in-florida-county-election-websites.webp" alt="Questions remain as tech company takes blame for glitch in Florida county election websites" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Questions remain as tech company takes blame for glitch in Florida county election websites</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      An elections technology company is taking full responsibility for glitches that kept many Florida county elections officials from immediately posting primary results Tuesday night.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/22/questions-remain-as-tech-company-takes-blame-for-glitch-in-florida-county-election-websites/"  >(The Associated Press, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 27 Aug 2024 21:21:50 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 27 Aug 2024 21:21:50 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Alex Gangitano, WFLA, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/27/harris-walz-to-give-first-joint-interview-to-cnn.webp" alt="Harris, Walz to give first joint interview to CNN" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Harris, Walz to give first joint interview to CNN</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Vice President Harris and Minnesota Gov. Tim Walz (D) will participate in their first joint interview with CNN on Thursday, the network announced. CNN’s Dana Bash will conduct the interview, which is set to air at 9 p.m.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/27/harris-walz-to-give-first-joint-interview-to-cnn/"  >(Alex Gangitano, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div></div></fieldset></main>
